@jezus1234. No bother, happy to help you complete your kink collections. We'll try to accomodate any re-seed requests.

Merzedes and I do what we can to ensure fast upload and seeding. We rely on other ppl to continue seeding once we move on to new uploads.

Did not realize how much time and effort goes into keeping you guys 'satisfied' until I started helping Merzedes out. Believe me, it is time consuming. 

Checking and rechecking our sources for updates. Downloading, renaming, unpacking, creating torrents, then uploading and, at times, manually managing seeding priority when required.

We love doing it, but the feedback and appreciation really helps to stay motivated :)
